@NODE nextv "VMB V2.0"


Planned features for VMB V2.0 :
===============================

        - text to voice! 
          for messages use normal ascii files instead of adpcm files.

        - Fax option like forwarding, back, ...

        - Callback Service

        - different Games... like the World Famous Hi-Lo Game! or Adventures

        - much better Control Tool with more features.


